long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introducing our innovative bookmark collector - With just one click, you can effortlessly collect bookmarks.

How to Use:
1. Sign up or log in.
2. Click the extension button on any website, or press Ctrl+E (Command+E on Mac).
We recommend pinning the extension icon for easier access.
Only http:// or https:// website can be collected, others are not supported.

Website: https://easy-nav.cc
